songs.title: Mood
songs.lyrics:
Wait, look how I am now
I do not know if you feel it

I feel like I'm dead from
A long time ago
I do not know if you know what I mean
No, you will not know

If you know how much I need you
I need you, I do not live without your being

Boy in need, that's me, yes
Yes, I am and I will be

If you knew what I need your love now
Now, and more than ever

My voice, my face, they hurt me

I need you here, here and now

Wait, look how I am now
I do not know if you feel it

I feel like I'm dead from
A long time ago
I do not know if you know what I mean
No, you will not know

If you know how much I need you
I need you, I do not live without your being

Boy in need, that's me, yes
Yes, I am and I will be

If you knew what I need your love now
Now, and more than ever

My voice, my face, they hurt me

I need you here, here and now

Come girl let's be happy
